#: ../../N/not-entirely-unlike-X.rst:5
msgid "not entirely unlike X"
msgstr "not entirely unlike X"

#: ../../N/not-entirely-unlike-X.rst:7
msgid ""
"Used ironically of things which are in fact almost entirely unlike X, except"
" for one feature which the speaker clearly regards as insignificant. \"That "
"is not entirely unlike cool...at least it's small.\" Comes directly from the"
" Hitchiker's Guide to the Galaxy scene in which the food synthesizer on the "
"starship *Heart of Gold* dispenses something \"almost, but not quite, "
"entirely unlike tea\"."
msgstr ""
"実際にはXとほとんどまったく似ていないものについて、話し手が明らかに取るに足らないと見なす一つの特徴を除いて、皮肉的に使われる。「あれは、まったくクールでないわけではない……少なくとも小さい」。これは『銀河ヒッチハイク・ガイド』の、宇宙船\\"
" *Heart of Gold*\\ "
"のフードシンセサイザーが「ほとんど、しかし完全にではないが、紅茶とまったく似ていない」何かを出す場面に直接由来する。"
